::Primal Prime::

    He was trying to figure out how to tell it. So he just started:
    "First off, I was in Autobot city on Earth. I was not myself, but someone 
else. I said to someone who looked like Megatron 'I thought you were made of 
sterner stuff'. Then you came and grabbed him. I was wisked away to the 
Matrix. I saw Cybertron as it should be, and how it will be, they are very 
different. I also saw Optimus Prime's spark travelling to the Matrix finally. 
This was in the future for us, it wasn't a past thing. I'm wondering what it 
means."
